mintxUSDC.t.sol
└── given user calls mintxUSDC function
    ├── when the input amount is invalid
    │   └── it should revert with TransferFailed()
    └── when the input amount is valid
        ├── when the amount breaks LTV
        │    └── it should revert with ExceedsLoanToValue()
        └── when the amount does not break LTV
             ├── it should update storage
             └── it should mint xUSDC
                    ├── when minting fails 
                    │   └── it should revert with MintingFailed()
                    └── when minting success
                        └── it should emit event 